    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ever wondered 'what if I was a tree'? Seek no further, Heliotropism is here.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653100/extras/3be8805faaaede01713aff6f1f981323.poster.avif?t=1664830342\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653100/extras/3be8805faaaede01713aff6f1f981323.webm?t=1664830342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653100/extras/3be8805faaaede01713aff6f1f981323.mp4?t=1664830342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this rogue-like tree-building game, your goal is to last long enough to bear fruit in a harsh environment. Grow your tree, manage your resources, obtain mutations, mitigate crises and survive cold winters to get to the fourth year.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653100/extras/a1f83214e64b291cd97284ead86099d0.avif?t=1664830342\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>Resource management</i>: Grow your tree carefully, spending energy that you generate to place tree parts so that you can generate more. Just beware of winter: no energy and no leaves means that the tree is dead<br></li><li><i>Evolve your tree</i>: As you go through the game, you can collect a plethora of mutations that not only make your tree stronger but change the optimal playstyle to something unique every run.<br></li><li><i>Unpredicted Challenges</i>: Survive different crises every playthrough, from a small breeze to forest fires, these are coming after your tree. Plan ahead and mitigate what you can, survival is not an easy task </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653100/extras/f2a457072e18ffc2082a2999c2628d13.avif?t=1664830342\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >To better suit your tree-growing needs, Heliotropism comes with:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Monthly updates<br></li><li> Customizable UI to fit your preferences.<br></li><li> 4 seasons with different effects on your tree<br></li><li> 100+ different mutations that buff up your tree in surprising ways<br></li><li> 10 Different crises to beat, as well as a challenging winter every year<br></li><li> 10 unlocks to enable even more content<br></li><li> A vast underground filled with aquifers, rocks and sigils<br></li><li> Hundreds of voice lines to keep you entertained while growing</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653100/extras/e2af32fa99a8377e674e4f21917cebe2.avif?t=1664830342\" width=600 height=150 /></span>",
